</table><div align="right"><a href="#top"><img src="img/article/top_link_0.gif" border="0" alt="" /></a></div><img src="img/leer.gif" width="1" height="10" alt="" /><br /><HR><br /><img src="img/leer.gif" width="1" height="25" alt="" /><br><span class="contentHead">Files &amp; Folder settings</span><br><img src="img/leer.gif" width="1" height="3" alt=""><br />You now need to setup the correct permissons for certain files and folders. This should be done using CHMOD from within your FTP Application.<BR><BR>
