</table><div class="articleText">To start the Installation process you open a new Browser window. Enter the address your phpWCMS files have been uploaded to including any sub-directories you may have used followed by /setup/index.php<BR>(e.g. http://www.YourDomain.com/YourSubDirs/setup/index.php)<br /><br /> After reading the License agreement click the <STRONG>I AGREE (CONTINUE)</STRONG> Button to accept the terms and conditions underwich to agree to abide. you will now be presented with a screen such as teh image left.</div><img src="img/leer.gif" width="1" height="25" alt="" /><br /><table width="158" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left" class="table_class">
